beer.beer_description:
A beer best paired with care free days, Side Track All Day XPA is the ideal go to beer for a moment of
refreshment on those days where the time just gets away from you.
Its packed with aromas of fresh citrus, tropical fruit (mango, pineapple) and a hint of pine, with a light malt base for a smooth body with crisp bitterness.
